"1013","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>A"
"1014","material weakness is a deficiency, or a combination of deficiencies, in"
"1015","internal control over financial reporting, such that there is a reasonable"
"1016","possibility that a material misstatement of the Funds&#8217; annual or interim"
"1017","financial statements will not be prevented or detected on a timely basis.</font></p>"
